As a researcher, I would prefer name and type fields to be hidden when not editing a 
researchers details within the account management interface, 
so that the page appears less cluttered
Labels: Avoid (High Risk/Low Value)
Moscow: Could
Story Points: 3

Background:  during the 2nd sprint review the stake holders asked whether it would be possible to
hide entry fields until after an 'edit' button is pressed.  this would also mean that a 
"Create New" button would have to be added in order to incorperate the add new function to the 
interface
